verbose_text: The proportion of patients with any psychiatric disorders did not moderate the associations between childhood trauma and CRP (t = 0.02, P = 0.98, I 2 res = 74.0%, tau 2 = 0.007), IL-6 (t = 0.23, P = 0.82, I 2 res = 48.5%, tau 2 = 0.006) or TNF-alpha (t = 0.54, P = 0.61, I 2 res = 42.7%, tau 2 = 0.01).
